headline: Truist Lifts Centene (CNC) Target to $49, Maintains Buy Rating After Positive Management Meetings
summary: Centene Corporation (NYSE:CNC) is included among the 14 Best GARP Stocks to Buy According to Analysts. On February 25, Truist raised its price recommendation on Centene Corporation (NYSE:CNC) to $49 from $47. The firm maintained a Buy rating on the shares.
